summary: He needs to look good for Camilla, right?
descriptionHtml: I just made Faendal\'s hair shoulder-length and chestnut. I also changed the nose because I have an obsession with noses. I started a playthrough where I wanted to have a sort of A-Team (Faendal is the Murdock of the group for some reason), and Faendal\'s looks did not fit in, but we needed an archer. So I fixed his head. God, I love it when a plan comes together.
author: Nonmeatbag
